    marketplaceDetailed: 'SDeal Marketplace\n\nSDeal is an international marketplace where sellers can offer their products to consumers in seven European countries. The platform combines the reach of a major sales channel with smart marketing automation. Sellers get full control over their prices, commissions and product offerings, while SDeal handles traffic, advertising and conversion optimization.\n\nThe strength of SDeal lies in the connection between performance marketing and marketplace sales. For each product, the set commission is directly used to attract targeted traffic, particularly via Google Shopping. Competitive prices and in-demand products are therefore automatically rewarded with more visibility.\n\nSDeal also offers sellers a repricer tool and an extensive dashboard to track sales performance and optimize prices. This way, sellers can compete on both price and performance, while the platform handles marketing.\n\nWe offer three options:\n\n1. Marketplace with fixed commission\nWith a fixed commission, you benefit from automatic marketing. SDeal handles traffic, advertising and conversion optimization.\n\n2. Marketplace with self-set commission\nWith your own commission setting, you also benefit from automatic marketing. SDeal handles traffic, advertising and conversion optimization.\n\n3. CPC (CaaS)\nWith Clicks as a Service, you pay a fixed monthly amount for visibility and traffic. No automatic marketing is performed.\n\nIn short: SDeal is a marketplace that not only sells, but actively grows with the performance of its sellers, transparent, scalable and fully focused on returns.',
