    dealCSSDetailed: 'DEAL CSS\n\nWith DEAL CSS, SDeal offers sellers the opportunity to advertise through our own Comparison Shopping Service (CSS), a Google-recognized comparison service.\n\nInstead of advertising directly through Google Shopping, the ad display runs through DEAL CSS. This is not only fully compatible with your existing Merchant Center, but also delivers direct benefits in Google\'s ad auctions.\n\nWhat is a CSS?\n\nA CSS (Comparison Shopping Service) is an independent party that displays product ads on behalf of webshops in Google Shopping. Since European competition rules require Google to share its Shopping space with external providers, sellers can advertise more cheaply through a CSS.\n\nWhy choose DEAL CSS\n\nUp to 20% lower click prices (CPC)\nGoogle offers a structural discount on clicks purchased through an external CSS. Sellers who advertise through DEAL CSS therefore directly benefit from lower costs per click.\n\nMore visibility with the same budget\nDue to lower click prices, you can generate more traffic with the same ad budget or perform better in Google Shopping\'s auction position.\n\nWorks independently of SDeal\nDEAL CSS works with your existing Merchant Center. Your current Merchant Center setup remains exactly the same. You only benefit from Google\'s discount on clicks purchased through an external CSS.\n\nTransparent and scalable\nYou retain insight into your performance and only pay the actual click or platform costs, without hidden commissions.\n\nIn summary\n\nDEAL CSS is the smart way to advertise your products through Google Shopping, with lower click prices, higher visibility and without extra complexity.',
